dc_title_s: Eastern Turkey in Asia. Sivas, sheet 8. Series I.D.W.O. no. 1522
dc_description_s: Great Britain. War Office. Intelligence Division. I.D.W.O. no. 1522. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. no. 1522. Relief shown by form lines and spot heights. Some sheets from this set were revised and issued by War Office. Geographical Section. General Staff, published as G.S.G.S. no. 1522, 1522a. Series covers Mesopotamia and eastern Anatolian parts of Ottoman Empire. "Compiled at the Intelligence Division, War Office by Major F.R. Maunsell, R.A. from Capt. F. Bennet 1883, Mr. Ellsworth Huntington 1901." With a glossary. Set is complete, see index.
